{"id": 1008, "genre": 1001, "title": "你身上也有这些“老好人病”的症状吗？", "description": "表面上友善无私，其实身心俱疲。（题图来自：Ryo Takemasa）", "record_count": 4685, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130034yxs5HQMGDVaeTOzB.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-29T01:25:55Z", "options": [{"id": 83200, "content": "雅虎吼吼他伙伴呢个", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623159}, {"id": 82945, "content": "不得不时常被倾诉，努力去安慰对方最后却被说“说的话都没一点意义”，一瞬间心累无以复加。", "image": null, "praise_count": 175, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136279}, {"id": 83201, "content": "经常把自己搞得很纠结", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627710}, {"id": 82946, "content": "老想告诉别人别走自己走过的歧途，但对方高傲的很，即使自己说了很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507134}, {"id": 83459, "content": "借钱，，，，\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 82948, "content": "经常被夸赞“你是个好人”", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527683}, {"id": 83204, "content": "真的不想再宽慰幼稚的人了。别再说那些矫情的事等别人安慰了，直接让我打死你好吗。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 82949, "content": "立场永远向着倾诉者", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199459}, {"id": 83205, "content": "就算自己满心不愿意也不想让别人失望", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627722}, {"id": 82950, "content": "多余的流星，呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590712}, {"id": 82951, "content": "多余的流星，呵呵。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590712}, {"id": 83207, "content": "有时自己明明很累，但不忍心拒绝别人的请求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623469}, {"id": 82952, "content": "多余的流星，呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590712}, {"id": 83208, "content": "不想帮还是帮了不想借还是借了 事后不断觉得自己是个傻逼并且暗自发誓下次绝不了 但是等下次再度发生之后结果还是重复 就是个死循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627685}, {"id": 82953, "content": "其实刚开始我是拒绝的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 320188}, {"id": 82954, "content": "永远在考虑自己做的事别人开心不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 792, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595150}, {"id": 83210, "content": "不会说no", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627748}, {"id": 86026, "content": "一个人做了件事明明让自己很不开心，却硬是逼自己原谅她！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575547}, {"id": 82955, "content": "别人总觉得你是万能的", "image": null, "praise_count": 287, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626702}, {"id": 83211, "content": "不想借给别人钱还是不忍心结果就会被←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612039}, {"id": 82956, "content": "不想给熟人设计logo", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574127}, {"id": 83212, "content": "太在意别人的想法，太纠结，太举棋不定", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627752}, {"id": 83468, "content": "因为乱七八糟技能太多所以每次都是团队最累的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470893}, {"id": 82957, "content": "我真的不想听了，可还是在听，得很仔细。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 213, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 84181}, {"id": 83213, "content": "为何  我 要顾及 那么多人  好累 真的好累", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319479}, {"id": 88845, "content": "唉 行吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219928}, {"id": 82958, "content": "不懂拒绝", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614600}, {"id": 83214, "content": "从不说出别人的缺点和毛病", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593366}, {"id": 83215, "content": "把别人的事看得比自己的事还紧张", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfec